snippet.title: Activeworlds Exploration Demo from 2007
snippet.description:
This is a demo of Activeworlds from 2007. It's an MMO where you can build anything with prefabricated objects. Things haven't changed much since I made this. Download #Activeworlds at activeworlds.com! 

SUBSCRIBE TO ME
https://www.youtube.com/SWChris?sub_confirmation=1

☺ ABOUT ME
I play games that "1-up life" in this positive way. I used to think I wasn't creative. And then video games happened. Games are a great way to express yourself, and your creativity begins with taking that first big step of just trying. I want to inspire you to take it!
